        <p style="font-size:0.88rem;color:var(--color-text-secondary);line-height:1.8;"><strong style="color:#6b4610;">Thinking about selling in Corinda?</strong> Daniel can give you an honest read on current conditions, what your property is likely to achieve, and what preparation will make the most difference to your result. No fluff, no obligation. <a href="/contact" style="color:#6b4610;font-weight:600;">Contact Daniel.</a></p>
      </div>

    </div>
